# LLM Configuration
# ====================

# Ollama Configuration (Recommended for local use)
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
OLLAMA_MODEL=mistral

# OpenAI Configuration (Optional - requires API key)
# Uncomment and add your OpenAI API key to use OpenAI instead of Ollama
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# Anthropic Configuration (Optional - requires API key)
# Uncomment and add your Anthropic API key
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-anthropic-api-key-here

# Data Processing Configuration
# ====================

# Titanic Exercise
